<subSubSection id="C3150DD102034A4F55817FA3FD6FFA7D" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB05E5A02034A4F55817FA3FD6FFA7D" blockId="4.[151,1436,1197,1510]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Comments: This species was described based on a single male specimen labeled “ 
<collectingCountry id="F3181ECA02034A4F51D67FA3FB18FB72" box="[1168,1241,1233,1257]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Brasil</collectingCountry>
.” 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E23AB02034A4F51B27FA3FA5DFB72" author="Drake" box="[1268,1436,1233,1257]" firstAuthor="Drake" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="111 - 118" refId="ref36172" refString="Drake, C. J. (1957 b) New neotropical water-striders (Hemiptera). Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 70, 111 - 118." type="journal article" year="1957" yearSuffix="b">Drake (1957b)</bibRefCitation>
described the species in December and mentioned that it was very similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F56B07F85FACCFA95" authority="Shaw, 1933" authorityName="Shaw" authorityYear="1933" box="[1014,1293,1270,1294]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kleopatra">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F56B07F85FB40FA95" box="[1014,1153,1270,1294]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. kleopatra</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E23AB02034A4F51CF7F84FACCFA95" author="Shaw" box="[1161,1293,1270,1294]" firstAuthor="Shaw" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="221 - 233" refId="ref43119" refString="Shaw, J. G. (1933) A study of the genus Brachymetra (Hemiptera - Gerridae). University of Kansas Science Bulletin, 21, 221 - 233." type="journal article" year="1933">Shaw, 1933</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, from which it differed in having an extremely long pronotum (3.50 mm) with apex “obtusely roundly subangulate.” 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F502F7E68FE93FACD" authorityName="Drake" authorityYear="1957" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="accola">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F502F7E68FE93FACD" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Brachymetra accola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is probably a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F57C27E4DFB81FACD" authority="Hungerford &amp; Matsuda, 1957" authorityName="Hungerford &amp; Matsuda" authorityYear="1957" box="[644,1088,1342,1366]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shawi">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F57C27E4DFD24FACD" box="[644,741,1342,1366]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. shawi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E23AB02034A4F57A87E4CFB81FACD" author="Hungerford &amp; Matsuda" box="[750,1088,1342,1366]" firstAuthor="Hungerford" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="19 - 25" refId="ref38392" refString="Hungerford, H. B. &amp; Matsuda, R. (1957) Description of two species of the genus Brachymetra (Gerridae, Hemiptera). Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society, 30, 19 - 25." type="journal article" year="1957">Hungerford &amp; Matsuda, 1957</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, described in January and also similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F54417E10FE51FAE1" authorityName="Shaw" authorityYear="1933" box="[263,400,1378,1402]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kleopatra">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F54417E10FE51FAE1" box="[263,400,1378,1402]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. kleopatra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
at first sight. In specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F57A67E10FC81FAE1" authorityName="Hungerford &amp; Matsuda" authorityYear="1957" box="[736,832,1378,1402]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shawi">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F57A67E10FC81FAE1" box="[736,832,1378,1402]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. shawi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
available for examination, the pronotum is about 3.50 mm and obtusely rounded, as described for 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F57387EF5FD26FA05" authorityName="Drake" authorityYear="1957" box="[638,743,1414,1438]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="accola">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F57387EF5FD26FA05" box="[638,743,1414,1438]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. accola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The paramere of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F56F37EF5FBDFFA05" authorityName="Drake" authorityYear="1957" box="[949,1054,1414,1438]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="accola">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F56F37EF5FBDFFA05" box="[949,1054,1414,1438]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. accola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not drawn by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E23AB02034A4F51B77EF4FA56FA05" author="Drake" box="[1265,1431,1414,1438]" firstAuthor="Drake" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="111 - 118" refId="ref36172" refString="Drake, C. J. (1957 b) New neotropical water-striders (Hemiptera). Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 70, 111 - 118." type="journal article" year="1957" yearSuffix="b">Drake (1957b)</bibRefCitation>
, but his description fits the general shape described and drawn for 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F56D37ED8FC39FA59" authorityName="Hungerford &amp; Matsuda" authorityYear="1957" box="[917,1016,1450,1474]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shawi">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F56D37ED8FC39FA59" box="[917,1016,1450,1474]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. shawi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The 
<typeStatus id="54B4E0F802034A4F51787EDBFB61FA5A" box="[1086,1184,1449,1473]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D902034A4F518D7ED8FAF6FA59" authorityName="Drake" authorityYear="1957" box="[1227,1335,1450,1474]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Brachymetra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="accola">
<emphasis id="B97B824802034A4F518D7ED8FAF6FA59" box="[1227,1335,1450,1474]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B. accola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
must be examined to confirm this hypothetic synonymy.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
